#. type: Plain text
#: origin/anti-spam-stuff.txt:144
msgid ""
"You get 4 tools, razor-check, razor-report, razor-revoke, and razor-admin, "
"each with it's own man page. The default log I have in "
"/var/log/razor-agent.log instead of a homedir, but it should be owned and "
"writable by the configured user"
