#. type: Plain text
#: origin/anti-spam-stuff.txt:184
msgid ""
"Vipul does not want any automatic reporting set up. One exception is if you "
"have mail adresses which you know are going to be 100% spam, as seeded "
"spamtraps, and you may indeed forward them. We will want to report manually, "
"being good netizens. Be aware that the checksums are on the body, as the "
"headers will differ anyhow. Further if you report spam sent to a mailing "
"list, you're a twit, because they usually add a footer, making the mailing "
"list copy different from the original. The list owner can report it, as he "
"gets an unmodified copy."
